Variables can be set at various places in the dialogue. For example, attached to replies:

[[Let it be "Four!"|Variables5|<<set $replyVariable = "Four!">>]]
[[I'm going for "Pizza."|Variables5|<<set $replyVariable = "Pizza.">>]]
[[I'll make it the number 8.|Variables5|<<set $replyVariable = 8>>]]
===
title: Variables5
tags: 
speaker: Bob
colorID: 0
position: 2069,76
---
So, your variable now has the value "$replyVariable" (without the quotes). 

